<section id="openReturnAuthorizations" role="standard">
  <title>List Return Authorizations</title>
  <para>To display open return authorizations by site, go to
  <guimenuitem>Sales &gt; Return Authorization &gt; List Open</guimenuitem>.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/openReturnAuthorizations.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>List Return Authorizations</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When displaying open return authorizations, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>All Sites</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display a list of open return authorizations for all
        sites.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify site whose open return authorizations you want to
        display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Unauthorized</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to include unauthorized returns in the display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Expired</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to include expired return authorizations in the
        display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Return Authorizations</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists open return authorizations.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
